**Ambitious workflows:** You're very close to a fully autonomous multi-agent pipeline where a single command spins up parallel agents in separate worktrees, each implementing a story, self-reviewing, and sequentially merging to main without intervention. As models get better at maintaining environment awareness and self-correcting, expect Claude to run terraform validate after every edit and automatically revert and retry when something breaks — turning your current manual revert cycles into a self-healing loop that never commits broken code. See _On the Horizon_.

